cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with indexing and retrieving documents based on relevance to a query pattern, which is a core problem in information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed index involves compressed full text indexing (cs.DS) and uses the term-frequency metric (cs.DB). The reduction in space involves logarithmic factors, which is a common theme in deep learning (cs.DL) and machine learning (cs.LG).
